<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">THIS&nbsp; SERVICES AGREEMENT (this &ldquo;Agreement&rdquo;) effective {{ date }} is between My Quick Startup LLC, doing business as GoPrep.com, a New York LLC with an address of 1622 Bay Ridge Avenue, Brooklyn, New York 11024&nbsp; (the &ldquo;Company&rdquo; or &ldquo;we&rdquo; or &ldquo;us&rdquo;) and, {{ companyName }}&nbsp; with an address of {{companyAddress}} (the &ldquo;Service Provider&rdquo; or &ldquo;you&rdquo;).&nbsp;</span></p>
